Kdo vám nařídil,
 abyste zabil mého otce?

294
00:33:20,540 --> 00:33:22,110
Kdo to byl?

295
00:33:26,950 --> 00:33:28,650
Han Tae Kyungu!

296
00:33:33,690 --> 00:33:35,660


297
00:33:44,910 --> 00:33:47,050
Yoon Bo Won.

298
00:34:02,070 --> 00:34:04,600
Proberte se!
Yoon Bo Won!

299
00:34:04,900 --> 00:34:07,080
Proberte se!

